+    /**
+     * Render the METS file section. This will contain a list of all bitstreams in the
+     * item. Each bundle, even those that are not typically displayed will be listed.
+     *
+     * <p>Example:
+     *
+     * <pre>{@code
+     * <fileSec>
+     *   <fileGrp USE="CONTENT">
+     *     <file ... >
+     *       <fLocate ... >
+     *     </file>
+     *   </fileGrp>
+     *   <fileGrp USE="TEXT">
+     *     <file ... >
+     *       <fLocate ... >
